WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.200
LaBrowser instruments real web behavior.

00:04.200 --> 00:12.433
Every click, every search, every chat prompt and response, every hesitation becomes structured data.

00:12.433 --> 00:19.966
Participants browse real websites in a dedicated research browser. Their normal browser stays untouched.

00:19.966 --> 00:29.000
You see the path: tabs, scrolls, prompts, responses, backtracks, and the decision that finally happens.

00:29.000 --> 00:36.200
And when the study needs an intervention, LaBrowser can change the live page condition.

00:36.233 --> 00:44.133
One group sees recommendation modules. Another sees them removed or labelled. The website is still the real website.

00:44.133 --> 00:51.400
No fake webshop. No fake chatbot. Real tasks, real pages, real behavior.

00:51.400 --> 00:58.800
LaBrowser: observe and shape the live web, then analyze the evidence.
